{
  "stem": "24212.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had all kinds of apartments rented for them because they had to wait two, three days in-- in Budapest or in Belgrade in the Czechoslovakian house.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in Budapest, while they were in these hired apartments, we didn't tell the Hungarians that they were Czechs because again, you have to know the central European mishmash.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Hungarians didn't like the Czechs, but they liked the Poles for historical reasons, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we said these are Poles, Polish refugees.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So of course, the Hungarians didn't know the difference when they heard the language.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Polish, Czech-- it was all the same to them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so I would go from one apartment to another to check if everything is all right or take ration tickets or take medicine, or take somebody to the dentist or whatever.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's when I was a-- messenger, I assume would be the closest.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And at one place I arrived, and the boys are saying, oh, we are in trouble!",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We are in trouble!",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The landlady wants us to sing the Polish National Anthem and no idea what the Polish National Anthem.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So, [LAUGHS] no problem, no problem.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You all know the song, [NON-ENGLISH], 'The Gypsy Girl,' which was an old sort of, you know, a popular song.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So slow it down, make a sad face, and sing [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we all stood there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The boys do this [INAUDIBLE] practically saluting.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we sang this popular song.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I should come up with something equivalent in English-- some silly song, you know, like, [SINGING] how much is the doggie in the window-- sad face.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The equivalent about the gypsy girl and her love.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the Hungarian landlady was satisfied.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Beautiful Polish anthem.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the crisis was over.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Yeah, I still remember that.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
